Language used : OCaml
Version       : 4.02.3

This directory contains a test of the get_token.ml function.

To run the test a Makefile has been included.

To conduct the test:

$ make test

The output to the screen should look like:

Begin of test
------------------

The string read was: result = (a+b)

Token alpha found: r
Token alpha found: e
Token alpha found: s
Token alpha found: u
Token alpha found: l
Token alpha found: t
White space found
Token BinOp found: =
White space found
Token found: (
Token alpha found: a
Token BinOp found: +
Token alpha found: b
Token found: )
Token BinOp found:

String is valid
------------------
End of test

